c=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F000920_61da7f6e44b927619060fe2fdb7ad314.png&h=0eb09539&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/000927_a982e6777209a6a2d7484a5bcc7b5688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F000927_a982e6777209a6a2d7484a5bcc7b5688.png&h=7e6dbdc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講野唔好咁離地啦<br />\n大陸係會FILTER廣告<br />\n但一樣會播TVB啲廣告<br />\n佢應該指定左邊啲廣告要播再額外收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6b2e0127e52c35a32b5b0dc28b35ad15878fed","tid":1064964,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f51fe71388f0eb0c88fd063771a4c02a95955e6","tid":1064964,"uid":30788,"like":15,"dislike":23,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"中共特登搞死粵語媒體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"自己一手造成"},{"pid":"4d2d8d7b03e2205cebbd71ec12460d1dc4100709","tid":1064964,"uid":54940,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"無埋自己電視台<br />\n<br />\n基本上個個地區既文化就正式玩完<br />\n<br />\n隨時係某國人叫公司自殺，再每個高層俾返幾億咁就得<br />\n<br />\n利申 發夢見到"},{"pid":"5f1c3ed7b9d27b35a70b1409e36b3d8c32b39b7c","tid":1064964,"uid":51720,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"b44a86c4d2502e0d61a8df4a77f58ece5908ecd6","tid":1064964,"uid":103230,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:27:47.000Z","msg":"以往一台獨大賺咁多啫⋯⋯<br />\n話就話盛世<br />\n但其實對樂壇至娛樂圈造成幾多傷害<br />\n而家係要還"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"最簡單去睇：1980年代至2000年代中後期，係粵語流行兒歌興盛時期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家嘅粵語兒歌幾乎全滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ef3b2cc38622c5e56397246d1f144336ece3c0","tid":1064964,"uid":54516,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"92ad97cc30bb8694958bfc0f294c60429451f851","tid":106